What is this mod doing?
  
  
Tit Kit is a collection of areola overlays, which you can find in the race menu under body painting. They can be customized through color settings, which makes the body more realistic and less boring. The overlays can also be used on NPCs through mods like [Standalone EFF Cosmetic Menu](https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/19353) and [The Manipulator SE](https://www.loverslab.com/topic/102776-the-manipulator-by-ffabris-for-se) (Loverslab). The Mod only works with CBBE.
  
In the screenshots you can see possible results of these settings. Many of you may already be using it, I uploaded it because I want to use it as a requirement for my mods.
  
  
I optimized the textures for SSE and converted the ESP (Form 44). I did the ESL conversion for myself a year ago and have been in my game ever since. If there are problems with it, please use the ESP variant.
